Exact opposite of Epic saga: async, eventual, choreographed.

The least coupled pattern

Services maintain their own transactional integrity

Doesn't work for complex workflow, stamp coupling may be used to fix that

Qualities
    Communication               Asynchronous
    Consistency                 Eventual
    Coordination                Choreographed
    Coupling                    Very low
    Complexity                  High
    Responsiveness/availability High
    Scale/elasticity            Very High